comments: Gordon (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Muscala (OKC) swipes down, but avoids making contact to Barton's (DEN) arm during his driving shot attempt,
Rivers (DEN) reaches in and makes contact with the ball last before it goes OOB. OKC maintains possession of the ball.
Muscala (OKC) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Rivers (DEN) is still moving laterally when contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Muscala (OKC) makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Dort (OKC) is late to the spot and initiates contact to Barton's (DEN) body at the end of the drive that affects his SQBR.
Barton (DEN) makes marginal contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Giddey (OKC) makes marginal contact with Gordon (DEN) attempting to commit a take foul.
